\(\[Lambda]\[Mu]\)]\)\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\()\), \(\[Dagger]\)]\) = \
(-1\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\()\), \(\[Mu]\)]\)\!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(T\), \(\
\[Lambda] - \[Mu]\)]\).\>\""}], ";"}], " "}]], "Input",
